<p>return preg_replace("/$pattern/sSD", '', $value);
=&gt;
return preg_replace("/$pattern/sSDu", '', $value);</p>

<hr /><p>u (PCRE8)
   This modifier turns on additional functionality of PCRE that is incompatible with Perl. Pattern strings are treated as UTF-8.</p>

